snippet.title: Bootleg Soldier Azure: ASTRAL RAVE v1.3.0
snippet.description:
Explode your way as Yuuto Ichika in her quest to get her cookbook back in Bootleg Soldier Azure: ASTRAL RAVE!

v1.3.0 is out now with a new letter grade ranking system for caravan mode and the option to adjust background brightness!

This game won 1st place overall in the Magical Girl Game Jam #9! Thank you for playing!

Play it for free here: https://crows-nest.itch.io/bootleg-soldier-azure

This game is a fan work of various LAME Dimension games and characters: https://lamedimension.moe/

This game contains arrangements of songs originally composed by Princess Sylvysprit: https://www.youtube.com/c/princesssylvysprit

// ---
